data.description: This lovely single family home has a spacious 2/2 floor plan with a den, 1 car garage, eat in kitchen, dining area, and a separate laundry off the kitchen. Located in the desirable 55plus community of Pine Ridge, amenities include pool, hot tub, tennis, shuffle board and more. Walk your pet easily through the community on side walks and get to know your neighbors. Property is partially furnished for easy move in, so schedule a showing today!
